'''Niantic'''（{{IPAc-en|n|aɪ|'|æ|n|t|ɪ|k}}）<ref name=ox>{{Cite web |url=http://www.oxforddictionaries.com/definition/english/niantic |title=Niantic - definition of Niantic in English from the Oxford dictionary |accessdate=2016-08-12 |archive-date=2016-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822040648/http://www.oxforddictionaries.com/definition/english/niantic |dead-url=no }}</ref>是[[美國|美國]][[加州|加州]]一家软件开发公司，知名产品为[[擴增實境|擴增實境]]游戏《[[Ingress|Ingress]]》<ref name="hanley">{{cite web|last1=Frank|first1=Blair Hanley|title=Google’s Niantic Labs merges another virtual world with reality in upcoming game|url=http://www.geekwire.com/2015/googles-niantic-labs-merges-another-virtual-world-with-reality-in-upcoming-game/|website=Geekwire.com|publisher=Geek Wire|accessdate=18 March 2015|archive-date=2015-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150818081801/http://www.geekwire.com/2015/googles-niantic-labs-merges-another-virtual-world-with-reality-in-upcoming-game/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=inc/>和[[寶可夢公司|寶可夢公司]]合作開發遊戲《[[Pokémon_GO|Pokémon GO]]》。

== 沿革 ==
前身Niantic Labs于2010年成立，由Keyhole, Inc.创办人John Hanke组建，作为[[Google|Google]]内部的[[创业公司|创业公司]]。<ref>{{cite web|last=Kessler|first=Sarah|title=Can A Startup Live https://nds-nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geofiksie Google? Niantic Labs, Creators Of Field Trip And "Ingress" Try|url=http://www.fastcompany.com/3004551/can-startup-live-inside-google-niantic-labs-creators-field-trip-and-ingress-try|work=Fast Company|accessdate=May 22, 2013|archive-date=2014-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140719154721/http://www.fastcompany.com/3004551/can-startup-live-inside-google-niantic-labs-creators-field-trip-and-ingress-try|dead-url=no}}</ref>公司名字取自[[加利福尼亞淘金潮|淘金热]]載運淘金客来到[[旧金山|旧金山]]的{{link-en|Niantic捕鯨船|Niantic (whaling vessel)}}，<ref name="inc">{{cite web|last1=Markowitz|first1=Eric|title=Exclusive: Inside the Mind of Google's Greatest Idea Man, John Hanke|url=http://www.inc.com/eric-markowitz/inside-the-mind-of-googles-greatest-idea-man.html|website=Inc.com|accessdate=19 June 2015|date=20 December 2012|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310041235/http://www.inc.com/eric-markowitz/inside-the-mind-of-googles-greatest-idea-man.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Upbin2012">{{cite web|last=Upbin|first=Bruce|title=The Niantic Project: What Is Google Up To?|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/bruceupbin/2012/11/08/the-niantic-project-what-is-google-up-to/|work=Forbes|accessdate=May 22, 2013|archive-date=2014-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140804181857/http://www.forbes.com/sites/bruceupbin/2012/11/08/the-niantic-project-what-is-google-up-to/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而「Niantic」又源自早期與[[歐洲|歐洲]]探險家接觸的[[印地安|印地安]]部落稱呼{{r|ox}}。

2015年8月，在Google宣布重组为[[Alphabet_Inc.|Alphabet Inc.]]后，Niantic也宣布脱离Google成为独立公司。<ref>{{cite web|last=Kessler|first=Sarah|title=Can A Startup Live Inside Google? Niantic Labs, Creators Of Field Trip And "Ingress" Try|url=http://www.fastcompany.com/3004551/can-startup-live-inside-google-niantic-labs-creators-field-trip-and-ingress-try|work=Fast Company|accessdate=May 22, 2013|archive-date=2014-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140719154721/http://www.fastcompany.com/3004551/can-startup-live-inside-google-niantic-labs-creators-field-trip-and-ingress-try|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=techcrunch>{{cite web|work=Tech Crunch|url=http://techcrunch.com/2015/08/12/niantic-labs-maker-of-ingress-spun-out-as-its-own-company/|title=Niantic Labs, Maker Of Ingress, Spun Out Of Google As Its Own Company|last=Olanoff|first=Drew|date=12 August 2015|accessdate=2015-08-27|archive-date=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825043725/http://techcrunch.com/2015/08/12/niantic-labs-maker-of-ingress-spun-out-as-its-own-company/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=fortune>{{cite web|work=Fortune|url=http://fortune.com/2015/08/13/googles-niantic-labs-spins-off/|date=13 August 2015|title=Google's internal start-up Niantic Labs spins off|last=Groden|first=Claire|accessdate=2015-08-27|archive-date=2015-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150820122631/http://fortune.com/2015/08/13/googles-niantic-labs-spins-off/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Ingress|title=Important Account Information: Niantic Labs is becoming an independent company...|url=https://plus.google.com/+Ingress/posts/GVvbYZzWyTT|accessdate=August 12, 2015|work=Ingress Google+ page|publisher=Google|archive-date=2019-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190314100937/https://plus.google.com/+Ingress/posts/GVvbYZzWyTT|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年10月宣布获得[[任天堂|任天堂]]、[[宝可梦公司|宝可梦公司]]和Google的2000万美元的先期投资。<ref>[https://www.nianticlabs.com/blog/niantic-tpc-nintendo/ Niantic Inc. Raises $20 Million in Financing from The Pokémon Company, Google and Nintendo] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nianticlabs.com/blog/niantic-tpc-nintendo/ |date=20160805100528 }}.Niantic Blog.2015-10-15.[2016-07-15].</ref>同年12月3日，成立日本法人{{nihongo|「株式会社Niantic」|株式会社ナイアンティック|Niantic K.K.<ref>{{Cite news |url = https://www.autobacs.co.jp/images/data/news/2016/04/27/A2sivf.pdf |title = AUTOBACS enters into the world of Ingress |newspaper =  |publisher = Autobacs Seven |date = 2016-04-27 |accessdate =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190217101140/https://www.autobacs.co.jp/images/data/news/2016/04/27/A2sivf.pdf |archive-date = 2019-02-17 |dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url =http://www.advertisingweek.asia/speakers/?id=5581&lang=en |title =Speakers: Setsuto Murai |publisher =Advertising Week Asia |date = |accessdate =2016-08-23 |deadurl =yes |archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160923000031/http://www.advertisingweek.asia/speakers/?id=5581&lang=en |archivedate =2016-09-23 }}</ref>}}。<ref>{{Cite news |url = http://www.famitsu.com/news/201512/03094421.html |script-title = ja:『Ingress』のNiantic, Inc.が日本法人“株式会社ナイアンティック”を設立 |newspaper =  |publisher = {{lang|ja|[[ファミ通|ファミ通]]}} |date = 2015-12-03 |accessdate =  |archive-date = 2016-08-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160813084322/http://www.famitsu.com/news/201512/03094421.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

2017年11月，Niantic宣布收购移动应用开发商Evertoon。<ref>[https://techcrunch.com/2017/11/03/niantic-acqui-hires-evertoon-to-add-a-social-network-to-pokemon-go-and-other-apps/ Niantic acqui-hires Evertoon to add a social network to Pokémon Go and other apps] {{Wayback|url=https://techcrunch.com/2017/11/03/niantic-acqui-hires-evertoon-to-add-a-social-network-to-pokemon-go-and-other-apps/ |date=20210304044153 }}.TechCrunch.2017-11-04.[2021-06-02].</ref>

==项目==
*2012年9月，Niantic推出了首个产品——一个[[Android|Android]]应用Field Trip。
*2012年11月，《[[Ingress|Ingress]]》推出。它是一个[[擴增實境|擴增實境]]Android游戏，在初期需要邀请才能注册。
*2013年10月，《Ingress》在Android平台上公开测试。
*2013年12月，《Ingress》正式在Android平台推出。
*2014年1月，Niantic Labs将会随一套书籍和电影推出新游戏《Endgame: Ancient Truth》，预计2014年内发售。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cnet.com/news/googles-niantic-follows-ingress-with-endgame/ |title=Google's Niantic follows Ingress with Endgame - CNET |accessdate=2014-07-20 |archive-date=2014-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140723002120/http://www.cnet.com/news/googles-niantic-follows-ingress-with-endgame/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*2014年7月，Niantic推出了《Ingress》的iOS版本。
*2015年9月10日，Niantic與[[寶可夢公司|寶可夢公司]]宣布合作开发 《[[Pokémon_GO|Pokémon GO]]》，為一智慧手機之擴增實境遊戲。
*2016年7月6日，《Pokémon GO》在澳大利亚和新西兰正式发售。
*2019年6月22日，Niantic与[[華納兄弟互動娛樂|華納兄弟互動娛樂]]合作開發的《[[哈利波特：巫师联盟|哈利波特：巫师联盟]]》正式推出<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://harrypotterwizardsunite.com/zh_hant/posts/|title=哈利波特巫師聯盟團隊|website=Niantic|access-date=2019-06-22|archive-date=2019-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190627093636/https://harrypotterwizardsunite.com/zh_hant/posts/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*2021年3月22日，Niantic和[[任天堂|任天堂]]宣布将开发一款基于《[[皮克敏|皮克敏]]》系列的增强现实智能手机游戏，游戏将预计于2021年下半年上线，将由Niantic位于东京的工作室制作。<ref>[https://www.theverge.com/2021/3/22/22345472/niantic-nintendo-pikmin-partnership-collaboration-ar-mobile-game Pikmin is the next AR game from the makers of Pokémon Go] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theverge.com/2021/3/22/22345472/niantic-nintendo-pikmin-partnership-collaboration-ar-mobile-game |date=20210518163112 }}.TheVerge.2021-03-22.[2021-05-08].</ref>
*2021年6月14日，Niantic宣布将与[[孩之宝|孩之宝]]以及TOMY合作推出一款《[[变形金刚|变形金刚]]》主题的增强现实智能手机游戏《变形金刚：重金属》（{{lang|en|Transformers: Heavy Metal}}）。<ref>[https://venturebeat.com/2021/06/14/transformers-heavy-metal-is-a-real-world-ar-mobile-game-from-niantic-and-hasbro/ Transformers: Heavy Metal is a real-world AR mobile game from Niantic and Hasbro].VentureBeat.2021-06-14.[2022-07-01].</ref>
*2021年10月27日，Niantic和[[任天堂|任天堂]]合作開發的《{{le|皮克敏Bloom|Pikmin Bloom}}》正式推出。
*2021年11月2日，Niantic宣布《[[哈利波特：巫师联盟|哈利波特：巫师联盟]]》将于12月下架各应用商店，并将于2022年1月31日停服。<ref>[https://www.cnet.com/tech/gaming/harry-potter-wizards-unite-is-shutting-down-early-next-year/ Harry Potter: Wizards Unite is shutting down early next year].CNET.2021-11-03.[2022-07-01].</ref>
*2022年6月28日，Niantic宣布将与[[NBA|NBA]]合作推出增强现实手游《NBA All-World》。<ref>[https://www.nba.com/news/niantic-nba-and-the-nbpa-team-up-for-nba-all-world Niantic, NBA and the NBPA team up for 'NBA All-World'].NBA.2022-06-28.[2022-07-01].</ref>
*2022年6月30日，Niantic宣布裁员8%，并同时宣布《变形金刚：重金属》和沉浸式体验戏剧《哈姆雷特》也将终止开发；另外代号“Blue Sky”和“Snowball”的内部项目也将取消。<ref>[https://chinese.engadget.com/niantic-layoffs-games-canceled-pokemon-go-100028227.html Niantic 裁員約 90 人，同時取消四項計畫].Engadget中文版.2022-06-30.[2022-07-01].</ref>

